 NON-DISCLOSURE AGREEMENT (\u201cAgreement\u201d) is made by and between the State of Maryland (the \u201cState\u201d), acting by and through _______________________________________ (Issuing Agency Name) (the \u201cDepartment\u201d or \u201cAgency\u201d or \u201cAuthority\u201d or \u201cCommission\u201d), and _____________________________________________ (the \u201cContractor\u201d).", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 373, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "a03b661c-533a-4d53-b809-d7237357e03f": {"__data__": {"id_": "a03b661c-533a-4d53-b809-d7237357e03f", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "023cf48a-cbba-4080-936e-20c662461ddc", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "eb8a7ba941a0329b6fd0d346fe25d600e1a2a8f37480124e1ec189f698af8eac", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "ed1570b1-2554-4cc8-8197-05054724fb72", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "4669aa3e887ddbe453b031a5c0d1e21e9aca126ba5c9eca3f3f58e0fd4dc8986", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "19ada707-f1d3-43c9-ab17-bfcec52d0a2e", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "18150c526ca2c41e478e3ecb63df33512ddc6212ae1aeac430ad1cd071a54d15", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "RECITALS\n\nWHEREAS , the Contractor has been awarded a contract (the \u201cContract\u201d) following the solicitation for ________________________________________________________ (Solicitation Title) Solicitation # ____________________; and", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 375, "end_char_idx": 604, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "19ada707-f1d3-43c9-ab17-bfcec52d0a2e": {"__data__": {"id_": "19ada707-f1d3-43c9-ab17-bfcec52d0a2e", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "023cf48a-cbba-4080-936e-20c662461ddc", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "eb8a7ba941a0329b6fd0d346fe25d600e1a2a8f37480124e1ec189f698af8eac", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "a03b661c-533a-4d53-b809-d7237357e03f", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "7ce98063bfdbed966e6f227e0a84198a14928c28dcd6a855fc6b411e3c71ff8a", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "b373b6c8-17a9-4328-90ae-eff0866e1e90", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "ca9454cda6a852e1b05b51ad390274b8fa631211f2f030090a9653d10c60f173", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "WHEREAS , in order for the Contractor to perform the work required under the Contract, it will be necessary for the State at times to provide the Contractor and the Contractor\u2019s employees, agents, and subcontractors (collectively the \u201cContractor\u2019s Personnel\u201d) with access to certain information the State deems confidential information (the \u201cConfidential Information\u201d).", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 607, "end_char_idx": 976, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "b373b6c8-17a9-4328-90ae-eff0866e1e90": {"__data__": {"id_": "b373b6c8-17a9-4328-90ae-eff0866e1e90", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "023cf48a-cbba-4080-936e-20c662461ddc", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "eb8a7ba941a0329b6fd0d346fe25d600e1a2a8f37480124e1ec189f698af8eac", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "19ada707-f1d3-43c9-ab17-bfcec52d0a2e", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "18150c526ca2c41e478e3ecb63df33512ddc6212ae1aeac430ad1cd071a54d15", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "4bcce103-992d-45f6-ab81-4fe032130df9", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "8b75067eb9040dbb763213793b59bd3b57ba88012131780f3c9ac0c7154d864e", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "NOW, THEREFORE , in consideration of being given access to the Confidential Information in connection with the solicitation and the Contract, and for other good and valuable consideration, the receipt and sufficiency of which the parties acknowledge, the parties do hereby agree as follows:\n1.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 978, "end_char_idx": 1271, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "4bcce103-992d-45f6-ab81-4fe032130df9": {"__data__": {"id_": "4bcce103-992d-45f6-ab81-4fe032130df9", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "023cf48a-cbba-4080-936e-20c662461ddc", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "eb8a7ba941a0329b6fd0d346fe25d600e1a2a8f37480124e1ec189f698af8eac", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "b373b6c8-17a9-4328-90ae-eff0866e1e90", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "ca9454cda6a852e1b05b51ad390274b8fa631211f2f030090a9653d10c60f173", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "426a3af6-5ebb-4ed6-96c8-01f4769926a4", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "7279f30a0b84e0e1769cf7e10dedce685aeef9db0ae1d93b4066460f2cf82c07", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Regardless of the form, format, or media on or in which the Confidential Information is provided and regardless of whether any such Confidential Information is marked as such, \u201cConfidential Information\u201d means (1) any and all information provided by or made available by the State to the Contractor in connection with the Contract and (2) any and all personally identifiable information (PII) (including but not limited to personal information as defined in Md. Ann.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1274, "end_char_idx": 1739, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "426a3af6-5ebb-4ed6-96c8-01f4769926a4": {"__data__": {"id_": "426a3af6-5ebb-4ed6-96c8-01f4769926a4", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "023cf48a-cbba-4080-936e-20c662461ddc", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "eb8a7ba941a0329b6fd0d346fe25d600e1a2a8f37480124e1ec189f698af8eac", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "4bcce103-992d-45f6-ab81-4fe032130df9", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "8b75067eb9040dbb763213793b59bd3b57ba88012131780f3c9ac0c7154d864e", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "cbed83c9-ae79-4f4f-bfec-fcb3b04b1d2f", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "c17963c021189d41c4e16eeeb37b11d69e6f557106ddb9300afa403edd7c9812", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Code, General Provisions \u00a74- 101(h) and Md. Ann. Code, State Govt. \u00a7 10-1301(c)) and protected health information (PHI) as defined in 45 CFR 160.103 that is provided by a person or entity to the Contractor in connection with this Contract.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1742, "end_char_idx": 1981, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "cbed83c9-ae79-4f4f-bfec-fcb3b04b1d2f": {"__data__": {"id_": "cbed83c9-ae79-4f4f-bfec-fcb3b04b1d2f", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "023cf48a-cbba-4080-936e-20c662461ddc", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "eb8a7ba941a0329b6fd0d346fe25d600e1a2a8f37480124e1ec189f698af8eac", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "426a3af6-5ebb-4ed6-96c8-01f4769926a4", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "7279f30a0b84e0e1769cf7e10dedce685aeef9db0ae1d93b4066460f2cf82c07", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "8e5d7985-eaae-47ee-8695-2ccfda0ef479", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "0f8510eee620a7e30f2d26ddad8205c517dfc012f0aca9a7db8be4fcd231bee0", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Confidential Information includes, by way of example only, information that the Contractor views, takes notes from, copies (if the State agrees in writing to permit copying), possesses or is otherwise provided access to and use of by the State in relation to the Contract.2.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1984, "end_char_idx": 2258, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "8e5d7985-eaae-47ee-8695-2ccfda0ef479": {"__data__": {"id_": "8e5d7985-eaae-47ee-8695-2ccfda0ef479", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "023cf48a-cbba-4080-936e-20c662461ddc", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "eb8a7ba941a0329b6fd0d346fe25d600e1a2a8f37480124e1ec189f698af8eac", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "cbed83c9-ae79-4f4f-bfec-fcb3b04b1d2f", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "c17963c021189d41c4e16eeeb37b11d69e6f557106ddb9300afa403edd7c9812", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "e056dc4a-7c6d-44b2-90f5-3ce891612cd1", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "5d20979b3cef95421da3ad432635cca558cbcdf8a181ad8acfa1883ccf29af3f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "The Contractor shall not, without the State\u2019s prior written consent, copy, disclose, publish, release, transfer, disseminate, use, or allow access for any purpose or in any form, any Confidential Information except for the sole and exclusive purpose of performing under the Contract.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2261, "end_char_idx": 2544, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "e056dc4a-7c6d-44b2-90f5-3ce891612cd1": {"__data__": {"id_": "e056dc4a-7c6d-44b2-90f5-3ce891612cd1", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "023cf48a-cbba-4080-936e-20c662461ddc", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "eb8a7ba941a0329b6fd0d346fe25d600e1a2a8f37480124e1ec189f698af8eac", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "8e5d7985-eaae-47ee-8695-2ccfda0ef479", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "0f8510eee620a7e30f2d26ddad8205c517dfc012f0aca9a7db8be4fcd231bee0", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "a525e70b-e8b5-47e0-9592-76342928c628", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "4d8a78760dc6d235d33f11de2bfd236eaf6080d86b62a339b4084ee87a21c9e5", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "The Contractor shall limit access to the Confidential Information to the Contractor\u2019s Personnel who have a demonstrable need to know such Confidential Information in order to perform under the Contract and who  are bound by confidentiality obligations at least as restrictive as those set forth in this  Agreement. Contractor shall provide copies of such agreements to the State.  The names of such personnel are attached hereto and made a part hereof as Attachment  I-2 .", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2547, "end_char_idx": 3019, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "a525e70b-e8b5-47e0-9592-76342928c628": {"__data__": {"id_": "a525e70b-e8b5-47e0-9592-76342928c628", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "023cf48a-cbba-4080-936e-20c662461ddc", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "eb8a7ba941a0329b6fd0d346fe25d600e1a2a8f37480124e1ec189f698af8eac", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "e056dc4a-7c6d-44b2-90f5-3ce891612cd1", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "5d20979b3cef95421da3ad432635cca558cbcdf8a181ad8acfa1883ccf29af3f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "cbae94d3-e2a2-4a6a-bfe9-8cb6918b6c72", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "b72501202de501c0a38dc14714e48397280a52b4860bfabb8aed0c40ec313c29", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Contractor shall update Attachment  I-2 by adding additional names (whether Contractor\u2019s Personnel or a subcontractor\u2019s personnel) as needed, from time to time.3. If the Contractor intends to disseminate any portion of the Confidential Information to non-employee agents who are assisting in the Contractor\u2019s performance of the Contract or will otherwise\nAttachment I \u2013 Non-Disclosure Agreement (Contractor) Page I-1\neffective date:  April 17, 2018", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3022, "end_char_idx": 3470, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "cbae94d3-e2a2-4a6a-bfe9-8cb6918b6c72": {"__data__": {"id_": "cbae94d3-e2a2-4a6a-bfe9-8cb6918b6c72", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "023cf48a-cbba-4080-936e-20c662461ddc", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "eb8a7ba941a0329b6fd0d346fe25d600e1a2a8f37480124e1ec189f698af8eac", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "a525e70b-e8b5-47e0-9592-76342928c628", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "4d8a78760dc6d235d33f11de2bfd236eaf6080d86b62a339b4084ee87a21c9e5", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "01ba48fc-ce2a-45aa-937f-97a2a9cc6609", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "1fe657e6f676ef0e09664933293da521690a1e59397380eb4de3ee6623224f1e", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "have a role in performing any aspect of the Contract, the Contractor shall first obtain the written consent of the State to any such dissemination. The State may grant, deny, or condition any such consent, as it may deem appropriate in its sole and absolute subjective discretion.4.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3473, "end_char_idx": 3755, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "01ba48fc-ce2a-45aa-937f-97a2a9cc6609": {"__data__": {"id_": "01ba48fc-ce2a-45aa-937f-97a2a9cc6609", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "023cf48a-cbba-4080-936e-20c662461ddc", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "eb8a7ba941a0329b6fd0d346fe25d600e1a2a8f37480124e1ec189f698af8eac", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "cbae94d3-e2a2-4a6a-bfe9-8cb6918b6c72", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "b72501202de501c0a38dc14714e48397280a52b4860bfabb8aed0c40ec313c29", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "7f35310b-b250-4c3d-b695-d5148ae17144", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "2c1e3ba6974f46deceeae39ad0c4b364ef3647f8fef71d55ebb5a74fed313c4d", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "The Contractor hereby agrees to hold the Confidential Information in trust and in strictest confidence, adopt or establish operating procedures and physical security measures, and take all other measures necessary to protect the Confidential Information from inadvertent release or disclosure to unauthorized third parties and to prevent all or any portion of the Confidential Information from falling into the public domain or into the possession of persons not bound to maintain the confidentiality of the Confidential Information.5.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3758, "end_char_idx": 4293, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "7f35310b-b250-4c3d-b695-d5148ae17144": {"__data__": {"id_": "7f35310b-b250-4c3d-b695-d5148ae17144", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "023cf48a-cbba-4080-936e-20c662461ddc", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "eb8a7ba941a0329b6fd0d346fe25d600e1a2a8f37480124e1ec189f698af8eac", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "01ba48fc-ce2a-45aa-937f-97a2a9cc6609", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "1fe657e6f676ef0e09664933293da521690a1e59397380eb4de3ee6623224f1e", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "5144cf96-5093-44b6-b7b0-ffe8f18020a0", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "fc8ca798c493e922b66167f1cc64dac8b26d8c2ab453045eb2cf37d8fe746d67", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "The Contractor shall promptly advise the State in writing if it learns of any unauthorized use, misappropriation, or disclosure of the Confidential Information by any of the Contractor\u2019s Personnel or the Contractor\u2019s former Personnel. Contractor shall, at its own expense, cooperate with the State in seeking injunctive or other equitable relief against any such person(s).6.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 4296, "